{"cursor":"7163","size":15,"audio":[],"currentlang":"en","article":"Lifelike is an adjective that relates to anything that simulates real life, in\naccordance with its laws. Its goal is to immerse individuals into what is called\na 'lifelike experience'. It gets as close as possible to real life behavior,\nappearance, senses, etc. therefore enabling its subject to experience what is\nhappening as if it were real. In other words, simulating reality with its\nphysical laws is the objective of lifelike experience.\n","linknr":127,"url":"Lifelike_experience","recorded":1362540585,"links":10,"instances":["franchise","film"],"pdf":[],"categories":["Simulation","Virtual reality","Augmented reality"],"headings":["Definition","Development","Examples","See also","Notes"],"image":["//bits.wikimedia.org/static-1.21wmf10/skins/vector/images/search-ltr.png?303-4","//bits.wikimedia.org/images/wikimedia-button.png","//bits.wikimedia.org/static-1.21wmf10/skins/common/images/poweredby_mediawiki_88x31.png"],"tags":[["world_builder","film"],["the_matrix","franchise"]],"members":["the_matrix","world_builder"],"related":["Real_life","Painting","Mona_Lisa","Trompe-l'Å“il","Photo","Digital_photography","Video","3-D_film","Haptic_technology","Force","Vibration","Perception","Prototype","Architect","Augmented_reality","Serious_game","Virtual_reality","World_Builder_(film)","The_Matrix_(franchise)","Inception","Defence_Centre_of_Training_Support","Die_Another_Day","Augmented_Reality","Computer-generated","Simulated_reality","Simulation","Video_game","Virtual_Reality"]}